the much faster did_multiplegt_dyn command, available from the ssc repository.
To estimate static effects, we strongly recommend using
the much faster did_multiplegt_stat command, available from the ssc repository.
In addition to speed gains, did_multiplegt_dyn and did_multiplegt_stat
also offer more comprehensive and up-to-date options than did_multiplegt_old.

DID estimators of the instantaneous treatment effect, of dynamic treatment effects
if the dynamic option is used, and of placebo tests of the parallel trends
assumption if the placebo option is used. The estimators are robust to
heterogeneous effects, and to dynamic effects if the robust_dynamic option is
used.

